Leave your comments below.

95
00:04:30,780 --> 00:04:32,800
Thanks for watching this episode of China
Uncensored.

96
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,570
Once again I’m your host Chris Chappell.

97
00:04:34,570 --> 00:04:35,970
See you next time.

